who.title: Who we are
who.p: We are a multinational logistics company with headquarters in New York City. Our main goal is that our buyers and sellers find the product they are looking for at the best price possible with the most efficient delivery service available. Our presence in multiple countries enables us to contact multiple distributors and factories all over the world to offer a broader number of brands and prices.
